s"},{"source":"recnE3a05RSOJchwR","target":"recGUuZfUbylFAytG","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recEsXmdzBins5yUr","ref":"Ezek.38.1","text":"And the word of the LORD came unto me, saying,","year":-587},{"id":"rec12RovwvAhyrIU9","ref":"Ezek.38.2","text":"Son of man, set thy face against Gog, the land of Magog, the chief prince of Meshech and Tubal, and prophesy against him,","year":-587},{"id":"recld31Fhl7AkN8pZ","ref":"Ezek.38.3","text":"And say, Thus saith the Lord GOD; Behold, I am against thee, O Gog, the chief prince of Meshech and Tubal:","year":-587},{"id":"recwZUQaLJ5agGqzn","ref":"Ezek.38.4","text":"And I will turn thee back, and put hooks into thy jaws, and I will bring thee forth, and all thine army, horses and horsemen, all of them clothed with all sorts of armour, even a great company with bucklers and shields, all of them handling swords:","year":-587},{"id":"recuuPEC3ieKG6sLp","ref":"Ezek.38.5","text":"Persia, Ethiopia, and Libya with them; all of them with shield and helmet:","year":-587},{"id":"recRfmeT8Tikg8Des","ref":"Ezek.38.6","text":"Gomer, and all his bands; the house of Togarmah of the north quarters, and all his bands: and many people with thee.","year":-587},{"id":"recJl0ppQnuFrJTfm","ref":"Ezek.38.7","text":"Be thou prepared, and prepare for thyself, thou, and all thy company that are assembled unto thee, and be thou a guard unto them.","year":-587},{"id":"recHDVfnBgWpLCxMc","ref":"Ezek.38.8","text":"After many days thou shalt be visited: in the latter years thou shalt come into the land that is brought back from the sword, and is gathered out of many people, against the mountains of Israel, which have been always waste: but it is brought forth out of the nations, and they shall dwell safely all of them.","year":-587}]}
